Association properties to be careful with: foreign_key, class_name, and source
source specifies source for a has_one :through association

EVENT
* date [datetime]
* location [string - doesn't need model]
* belongs to host (foreign key: user)

INVITATION
* belongs to event [no connection to host particularly - not needed]
* belongs to invitee (foreign key: user)
* has one host through event (this is where source comes in)
* status: pending, accepted, or rejected

USER
* has many hosted events
* has many attending events (through invitation)
* name (string)
